00:02:08,273 --> 00:02:11,673
 It's time for your first try.

33
00:02:12,366 --> 00:02:16,366
 F.P.R. Training

34
00:02:18,266 --> 00:02:23,026
 Now, please try to express the Japanese I say in English within the time limit.

35
00:02:25,026 --> 00:02:28,726
 Boil the hot water and try to say it in English, please.

36
00:02:34,726 --> 00:02:37,826
